11068257052639322639.Text: Adusamsi Assurnarairan asked me to recover her ring from Llaren Terano, the sorcerer who captured her. She doesn't sound quite right in the head. She thinks the sorcerer may have poisoned her mind with spells. She says she can use the enchantments to escape. She asked me also to free the slaves here. Llaren Terano has their slave key.

21377191231692810857.Text: I recovered Adusamsi's Ring and returned it to her. I suppose she will use its Divine Intervention enchantment to escape. Now I can return to the Oracle and report having completed my task. And I should also bring her the Ice Blade of the Monarch, if I can find it.
